\end_inset

 in which every pair of distinct vectors is orthogonal is linearly independent.
 Suppose 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{1}\mathbf{v}_{1}+c_{2}\mathbf{v}_{2}+\cdots+c_{p}\mathbf{v}_{p}=\mathbf{0}$
\end_inset

 for scalars 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{1},c_{2},\ldots,c_{p}$
\end_inset

.
 Then
